        "text": "Before the account of his death, a few other notices respecting his family are introduced for the purpose of preparing the way for the following history of the doings of his sons, in which the sin of Gideon came to a head, and the judgment burst upon his house. \"And Jerubbaal, the son of Joash, went and dwelt in his house.\" Both the word ויּלך, which simply serves to bring out the fact more vividly (see the remarks on ",
